Third Department,

July, 1986

(July 2, 1986) The People of the State of New York, Plaintiff, v William R. Force, Defendant.

— Motion, pursuant to CPL 460.30, for extension of time to take appeal denied (see, People v Kaczynski, 119 AD2d 927). Mahoney, P. J., Kane, Weiss, Yesawich, Jr., and Levine, JJ., concur.
